@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
control "Dispatcher" as D
participant "Customer" as C
actor "Driver" as D2
control "Fleet Manager" as FM
D2 ->> C : Update Inventory
note over C : processing update inventory
FM --> D2 : Schedule Pickup
D --> FM : Assign Route
activate FM
FM --> D : ACK
deactivate FM
note over FM : processing assign route
FM ->> D2 : Deliver Package
activate D2
D2 --> FM : ACK
deactivate D2
D ->> D2 : Load Package
note over D2 : processing load package
C -> FM : Report Issue
D ->> FM : Track Shipment
@enduml